Uwaga Highlander				KEY:Uwaga Highlander_Trait								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait																													DESC:You were born and raised in western Katapesh, in the rugged badlands and hills of the Uwaga Highlands. Even if you were born in a city like Solku, you often had to travel the dangerous trails with your family. Predators, gnolls, and worse haunt the Uwaga Highlands, and you've become something of an expert at evading them.																																																																			BONUS:SKILL|Hide,Move Silently|1|TYPE=Trait																SOURCEPAGE:p. 7

